✅ Ad card deal animation.

Ad conversations engine. Conversations between AI's, between dealer and ai's, Sometimes the ai can ask us questions, even when we aren't seated, to which we have to respond. If we choose to igbore them that raises the suspicion meter, like we are concentrating to hard. Conversation bubbles to appear above avatar, can cover cards.

Raising and dropping bets at certain points also raises suspicion, moreso if the count is high. Doing so with a poor count lowers suspicion.

The ai's have a percentage for how they play in regards to perfect play.

